title: Tentacles Enter the Dolphin APK FULL+MOD
description:
Mod apk with obb, full game, DLC included. Version 1.0

Localized for Brazilian, Portuguese, French, German, Italian, Spanish

Key Features:-

Challenging 3D animated levels with tons of dangerous hazards.
Addictive game play with amazingly intuitive tap controls.
Awesome boss fights Receive rewards for your skills.
Score big as collect pick ups and clear speed and damage challenges.
Achievements system.
Easy mode.

The optional Dog Eat Dog expansion gives you:

New electrifying game play mechanic.
New enemies to satisfy your apetite.
15+ levels in brand new world.
2+ new bosses to beat.
Another chapter in the absurd story of Dr. Phluff
